<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1214] differentiate between solr home and instanceDir</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1214</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a lot of confusion on what is an instanceDir in a multicore system. The CoreContainer must have a field for solrHome  and the instanceDir for each core should be specific to that core&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12427555">SOLR-1214</key>
            <summary>differentiate between solr home and instanceDir</summary>
